columns.expression: CASE WHEN state = 'CA' THEN num ELSE 0 END

queryData.query:
SELECT state AS state,
       gender AS gender,
       name AS name,
       sum(num) AS total,
       sum(sum_boys) AS `SUM(sum_boys)`,
       sum(sum_girls) AS `SUM(sum_girls)`,
       1.0 * SUM(sum_boys) / SUM(num) AS pct_boys,
       sum(num) AS `SUM(num)`
FROM birth_names
GROUP BY state,
         gender,
         name
ORDER BY `SUM(num)` DESC
LIMIT 50000
